          <p class="h3-heading-pp">
            AI Assistance
          </p>
          <p class="body-text">
            Our technology leverages a large reference database of authentic and counterfeit samples to support expert authenticators, improving routing, consistency, and workflow efficiency while all authentication decisions remain human-led.
          </p>
